name: sha256
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sha256" %}
{% set version = "0.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/sha256-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7bf2d287c2df10af1b7e6830340beeb1a79edc0433740f2e4fc68d8c1d06ab95

build:
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 2

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - cython
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - sha256
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/sha256/
  summary: sha256 library with midstate
  dev_url: https://github.com/cloudtools/sha256
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jan-janssen
